@startuml recommendation-generation
title Recommendation Generation Flow
actor User
participant "Platform\nBackend" as Backend
participant "Financial Profile\nService" as Profile
participant "Portfolio Analysis\nEngine" as Portfolio
participant "Risk Profiling" as Risk
participant "Asset Allocation\nModels" as Allocation
participant "Fund Ranking" as Ranking
participant "Recommendation\nEngine" as RecEng
participant "Suitability\nValidation" as Suitability

User -> Backend : Recommendation request
Backend -> Profile : Get user financial profile
Profile --> Backend : Financial profile
Backend -> Portfolio : Analyze portfolio
Portfolio --> Backend : Portfolio analysis
Backend -> Risk : Get risk profile
Risk --> Backend : Risk profile
Backend -> Allocation : Determine target allocation
Allocation --> Backend : Allocation targets
Backend -> Ranking : Get ranked products
Ranking --> Backend : Ranked products
Backend -> RecEng : Generate recommendations
RecEng -> RecEng : Filter, select, distribute
RecEng -> Suitability : Validate recommendations
Suitability --> RecEng : Approved / adjusted
RecEng --> Backend : Recommendation output
Backend --> User : Recommendations
@enduml
